{"tid":35390,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透]電影「你的名字。」隱藏結局","createTime":"2016-12-12T05:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T16:46:28.000Z","uid":130,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee14278eab9e02c1bc78accfaadde6098b2e2bf1","tid":35390,"uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"最後一幕，<br />\n三葉同瀧齊聲問&quot;你叫咩名？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n「三葉，宮水三葉」<br />\n「瀧」<br />\n<br />\n曾經消失的記憶，交換時日常趣事，合力拯救整村人的回憶都隨對方的名字在腦內浮現出來了。<br />\n<br />\n瀧：「三葉！」<br />\n三葉：「瀧！」<br />\n<br />\n兩人在樓梯間相擁，淚如泉湧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三葉：「瀧，我隻豬幾年前已經俾個mk呃左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n瀧：「 ....... 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「Bye」</span>"},{"pid":"327e3a0f7b5c76d34e88265d9ace1fe922425350","tid":35390,"uid":1052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05e023e5ddef5b4451f6c25f9ed6225daeb86fb","tid":35390,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6218414cf2512001c910225db6f0beadbe120bc6","tid":35390,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class